<heading>delete - Delete a contact.</heading>
<rule/>
<heading level="2">Usage</heading>
<pre>delete NAME</pre>
<heading level="2">Description</heading>
<paragraph>Permanently removes a contact.</paragraph>
<paragraph>This action cannot be undone.</paragraph>
<heading level="2">Examples</heading>
<pre>delete John
  Delete the contact John.</pre>
<heading level="2">See also</heading>
<paragraph>add, edit, find, list, show</paragraph>
